Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.29,0:00:01.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,《超感警探》前情提要
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.75,0:00:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她说血腥约翰左肩膀有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.40,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,三个点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.87,0:00:08.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我的筹码
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.56,0:00:11.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把五名疑犯同时
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.29,0:00:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,集合到一个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.23,0:00:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后再检查是否有纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.15,0:00:15.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何才能做到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.22,0:00:17.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-周四晚上八点见面  -好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.98,0:00:19.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周四晚上八点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.55,0:00:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我需要你的帮助  -没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.82,0:00:24.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你如果不去  他就会认为你是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.35,0:00:26.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我如果去了  你和简
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.93,0:00:28.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不会再怀疑我是血腥约翰了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.78,0:00:30.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以后绝对不会了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的确定了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:34.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-是的  -此案结束的时候我要在场
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就等您这句话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.81,0:00:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.50,0:00:39.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚我若能去见你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.34,0:00:41.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是再高兴不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:44.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰  有个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.17,0:00:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左臂上有三个点  就在肩膀上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.02,0:00:52.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们都得
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.61,0:00:54.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我看
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.69,0:00:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立刻动手
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.37,0:01:04.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开始脱吧  快
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:08.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.43,0:01:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太荒唐了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.10,0:01:22.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.20,0:01:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.48,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.64,0:01:34.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.03,0:01:38.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  派翠克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:39.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看  这边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.60,0:01:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.41,0:02:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到他们俩那边去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.15,0:02:08.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们别动
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:10.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了  你们三个
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到墙边站着  快
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.36,0:02:22.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等  不要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:59.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快叫消防部门和急救人员过来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.06,0:03:01.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉他们这里有多人伤亡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.02,0:03:01.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警戒线拉起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:02.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-把你的手电筒给我  我进去  -给你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.80,0:03:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.51,0:03:27.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探员
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.68,0:03:28.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探员  我是特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.90,0:03:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你没事吧  -发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.11,0:03:33.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里刚刚发生了爆炸  急救人员已经在路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.66,0:03:34.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会救治你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.80,0:03:40.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不许动  -什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.29,0:03:41.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把手举起来
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然我就开枪了  快
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.19,0:03:45.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  我不明白你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.39,0:03:46.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你明显搞错了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.79,0:03:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯往哪边走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.29,0:04:00.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天哪  里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.19,0:04:02.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿  我们必须得找到史密斯  他是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.92,0:04:04.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去找人帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.84,0:04:07.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能听到我讲话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.26,0:04:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  快醒醒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.18,0:04:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生说简的情况稳定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没受什么重伤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他只是醒不过来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.38,0:05:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现场发现了三个人的残骸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.03,0:05:06.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,化验确认是布莱特·斯特尔斯  雷·哈弗内
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.11,0:05:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和托马斯·麦卡利斯特的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:08.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.06,0:05:10.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为核攻击都干不掉布莱特·斯特尔斯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,尸体都被烧焦了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但鉴证科还是提取出了DNA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.59,0:05:16.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,验尸官那边将结果与医疗记录进行比对
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.48,0:05:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已确认三位死者正是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,斯特尔斯  哈弗内和麦卡利斯特
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.26,0:05:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那史密斯呢  有人看到他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.03,0:05:23.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没  瑞斯比和范佩尔正在查
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:52.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,长官
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.77,0:05:54.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就知道在这儿能找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.10,0:05:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.10,0:05:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没事  不过我确实得喝杯咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:58.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能帮我去买一杯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.74,0:06:01.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们马上要开始联合追捕史密斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.21,0:06:02.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你该赶快去抓他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.86,0:06:04.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我更想待在这里  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你是...  -周和其他组员应付得来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.30,0:06:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是要拒绝执行我的命令吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.29,0:06:09.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只是想在这里陪他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:12.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你给我听清楚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.02,0:06:13.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我命令你现在马上离开
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带领你的组员一起去抓捕史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.10,0:06:20.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  简  那个呼叫按钮在哪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.38,0:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去叫护士
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.63,0:06:24.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.18,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:13.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们现在认为  是血腥约翰带去的炸弹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.00,0:07:14.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要杀死简和其他嫌犯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.57,0:07:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧  但怎么布下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.44,0:07:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是血腥约翰随身偷偷带进去的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.87,0:07:19.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犯罪现场小组从墙上发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,炸弹外壳的碎片  碎片非常小
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.57,0:07:24.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这说明火药密度高  威力很大
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.63,0:07:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那肯定不是自制的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.69,0:07:26.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  我猜是军用级别的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.98,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就说明我们能够追踪到来源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.35,0:07:30.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些是最有可能的来源
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.11,0:07:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查查看最近他们中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:33.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有谁曾报告丢失过炸药
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.94,0:07:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  马上去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.02,0:07:36.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-有线索了吗  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.23,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本在史密斯逃走前曾击中过他
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是带着枪伤在四处逃窜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.22,0:07:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医院看到枪伤必须向警方报备
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.94,0:07:43.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他不能去看急诊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.28,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  他需要一个不会声张的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯一直在萨克拉门托工作
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.36,0:07:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我查了一下全市他负责过的案件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他所在的缉毒小组
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.06,0:07:52.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去年在萨克拉门托市南部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.54,0:07:54.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓捕过阿列克·拉夫罗夫医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个非法开具奥施康定[强力止痛药]处方的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.18,0:07:56.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}Dr. Feelgood指的是常给病人开出兴奋剂等安慰性药方的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.81,0:07:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-然后呢  -案子审判不顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.83,0:08:00.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,证物丢失  拉夫罗夫被无罪释放
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.76,0:08:02.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以史密斯很清楚在哪能找到一位
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.28,0:08:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会报警的医生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:04.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好  我们马上去查
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.83,0:08:16.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你想的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.59,0:08:17.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.78,0:08:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,派翠克  等等  看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.78,0:08:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.49,0:08:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.05,0:08:49.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你家里发生了爆炸
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.03,0:08:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我昏迷多久了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.83,0:08:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十二个小时
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.85,0:08:56.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.66,0:08:58.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到他肩膀上的纹身了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.52,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不只他有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:03.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麦卡利斯特身上也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.88,0:09:06.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他已经死了  斯特尔斯和哈弗内也死了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.05,0:09:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-还有伯特仑  -伯特仑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.84,0:09:11.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他也有那个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.45,0:09:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的天
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:15.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚才还在这
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.70,0:09:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他刚才就站在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.92,0:09:18.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他  他还一直想让我离开
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是要杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:21.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我的衣服呢  -别着急  好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事  我们没有时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.02,0:09:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简  简
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.28,0:09:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.40,0:09:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:31.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在全州境内发出里德·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和盖尔·伯特仑的通缉令
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  就是伯特仑局长
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接近时务必小心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.08,0:09:39.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们持有武器  十分危险
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.55,0:09:41.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们其中一个就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.99,0:09:43.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}伊凡·拉夫罗夫医生诊所
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.89,0:09:45.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体简体\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}今日停业
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:59.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请赶快离开  女士  警察办案
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.12,0:10:07.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.96,0:10:09.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,子弹还在你体内
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.76,0:10:11.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别废话了  赶紧取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.55,0:10:15.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会很疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.98,0:10:18.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定不吃点止疼药
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.57,0:10:19.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.79,0:10:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吃  我要保持警觉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就随你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.83,0:10:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.79,0:10:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.59,0:10:43.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.59,0:10:45.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯在这
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.48,0:10:47.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  他快喊破喉咙了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.60,0:10:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不会成为麻烦的  你打算怎么做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.91,0:10:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚从加调局得到消息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:54.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有几个探员正要来这里找史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.23,0:10:55.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-那我们该怎么办  -赶紧了事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:58.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你进去搞定他  加调局的人来了我拖住他们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.67,0:10:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从后面把他带出去  在那干掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他逼我这么做的  我是无辜的  -闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.66,0:11:20.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他一走我就会报警的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:21.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不想惹麻烦  -闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.40,0:11:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也是组织的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎  你为什么不给我们打电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:30.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说来真怪  因为我不相信你们
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:32.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要信任你的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.70,0:11:35.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来帮你的  你能走路吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.41,0:11:37.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得给他缝好  不然会失血的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.04,0:11:39.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我能走路
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.35,0:11:58.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是科德罗警探  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.08,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比探员
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.80,0:12:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他是萨城警局的  负责柯克兰枪击案
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.72,0:12:05.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是格蕾斯·范佩尔探员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.47,0:12:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们怎么来萨城南部了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.92,0:12:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们跟一条线索过来抓里德·史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.37,0:12:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是  血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.02,0:12:13.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来我们快你们一步
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.51,0:12:15.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人已经进去抓他了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.70,0:12:16.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,需要我们看住后面吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.61,0:12:19.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-不用  我们能搞定  -你确定
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.23,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我们不是加调局的  但是我们也是警察
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:24.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.79,0:12:28.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.93,0:12:30.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑞斯比  你在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.19,0:12:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在医生办公室外面  史密斯好像在里面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有警察在你身边吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.50,0:12:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.64,0:12:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  你仔细听清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要相信任何一名执法人员
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.58,0:12:41.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁也不能相信  明白吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.81,0:12:42.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.55,0:12:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们去后面四周看看
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.38,0:12:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.47,0:12:51.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们去哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.30,0:12:53.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,车就在这边
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.90,0:12:54.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切都安排好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:57.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在附近有个安全屋  干净衣服  一名医生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:58.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出城的路线也准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:01.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安全屋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.75,0:13:04.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也对某个人说过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:07.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  后来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.10,0:13:10.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我朝他后背开了六枪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.45,0:13:14.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖乖就范吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.59,0:13:19.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:39.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:02.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你没事吧  -没事  你还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.69,0:14:03.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.62,0:14:12.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯趁乱逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.24,0:14:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个警探也是
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿  他们想杀史密斯和我们  这是为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.99,0:14:18.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我不知道  -看看他的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.31,0:14:20.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-什么  -让他看看左肩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.31,0:14:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让瑞斯比把他衬衣脱了看他的肩膀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.70,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里斯本想让你看他的左肩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.04,0:14:31.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.81,0:14:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有  他肩上有那个纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.35,0:14:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿  这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  把他带回局里
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.45,0:14:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别让任何人接近他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:40.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.51,0:14:57.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查到袭击你们的警察身份了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.28,0:14:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我们抓到的那个  保罗·魏海根警官
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.87,0:15:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当警察六年  模范警察
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.83,0:15:04.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受过几次表彰  没纪律问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.31,0:15:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那另一个  科德罗警探呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打电话问了他队长
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.29,0:15:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说他一小时前请了病假
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.66,0:15:09.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是没查到伯特仑的行踪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:11.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就着重调查我们抓到的这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.45,0:15:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或许简会弄清真相
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.99,0:15:16.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人派你杀里德·史密斯吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.53,0:15:19.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无可奉告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.90,0:15:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为什么要杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那纹身是怎么回事  有什么意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.09,0:15:34.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不善言辞  我懂
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.03,0:15:37.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,祸从口出嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.42,0:15:39.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,坏消息是  你的表情控制得不够好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.63,0:15:42.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我们要玩个你演我猜的小游戏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.97,0:15:44.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我告诉你些事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:46.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你用表情告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.50,0:15:48.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是对是错
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.39,0:15:49.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有意思吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.10,0:15:52.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你偷过东西吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.59,0:15:56.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你背着女友偷腥过吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:58.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打过她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.42,0:16:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢施暴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:02.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我从没打过女人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.99,0:16:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一个由警察和其他政府官员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组成的秘密组织成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.19,0:16:10.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:14.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你为维护那个组织的利益犯过罪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.97,0:16:17.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.05,0:16:21.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探员也是组织成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.97,0:16:24.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.50,0:16:28.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织派你去那个诊所杀他
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.81,0:16:34.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加调局局长盖尔·伯特仑也是组织成员
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.79,0:16:37.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.20,0:16:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等级太低了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.78,0:16:43.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯探员是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.47,0:16:45.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.29,0:16:48.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔·伯特仑是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.22,0:16:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.61,0:16:56.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肩上的纹身是组织成员的标志
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.60,0:17:00.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.48,0:17:01.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又对了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.28,0:17:05.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有个暗号
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:07.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你们成员间用来识别身份
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.81,0:17:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和求救的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.35,0:17:13.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.43,0:17:17.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从我脑子里滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.43,0:17:20.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个腐败警察的秘密组织
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰是成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.42,0:17:24.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帕特里奇
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:26.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他死之前对我说了"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.96,0:17:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  没错
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.36,0:17:30.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在求救
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.12,0:17:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,寄希望于你也是成员之一
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.28,0:17:34.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是如果他也有纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,验尸报告里应该有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:37.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能相信什么报告
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要亲眼看到才行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.66,0:17:40.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会让周去检查尸体
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.74,0:17:42.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是很有可能帕特里奇已经下葬了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.58,0:17:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就让周带上铲子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.09,0:17:46.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们的人在找史密斯  伯特仑在外逃中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.77,0:17:47.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底谁是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:49.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是伯特仑还是史密斯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.47,0:17:53.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要看着他们的眼睛才能确定
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.53,0:17:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,验尸官两天前把尸体送过来的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.12,0:18:00.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-谋杀案被害人是吧  -是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:02.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我猜就是  所以才会一直留着他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:04.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幸好你今天来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.14,0:18:07.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就什么都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.92,0:18:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布雷特·帕特里奇
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.35,0:18:11.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮把手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.37,0:18:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.33,0:18:35.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把刀给我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.52,0:18:45.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烧之前都会给他们穿上好衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.28,0:18:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不知道为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.39,0:19:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,周发了张照片过来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:11.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说明什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.70,0:19:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得这说明什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.45,0:19:21.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯处理好了么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.65,0:19:24.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们差点就在诊所那里解决他了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:26.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加调局的人来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.53,0:19:28.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.18,0:19:29.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可真会跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:33.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这儿等我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.06,0:19:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  托马斯先生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.71,0:19:46.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您很久没来了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:47.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很高兴见到你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.50,0:20:43.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯现在可能在任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:45.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我试着追踪他手机上全球定位信号
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.91,0:20:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经关闭好几个小时了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.29,0:20:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,像他这样的腐败联调局警察一定会有一次性手机
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.64,0:20:51.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拉夫罗夫医生说他还没缝合史密斯的伤口
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.74,0:20:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他现在还带着枪伤四处走动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么不管他在哪儿  情况一定不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最终一定会被人发现的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.09,0:20:58.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  但是发现他的警察
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太可怕了  我们谁都不能信
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.60,0:21:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩尔探员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.47,0:21:54.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.63,0:21:55.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯探员
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.97,0:21:57.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们会杀了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.81,0:21:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要自首
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.85,0:21:59.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.22,0:22:03.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}第十八大道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.68,0:22:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在市中心  给周打电话  他应该在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.25,0:22:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  我们这就来
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.63,0:22:16.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,史密斯联系加调局了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.46,0:22:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他用了组织给他的一次性手机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.84,0:22:19.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们监听了那部手机
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.71,0:22:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要自首
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.90,0:22:22.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.48,0:22:24.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加调局的人去接他了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.28,0:22:25.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可不行  他在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.96,0:22:28.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离这儿不远的小巷子里  我们运气很不错
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.72,0:22:29.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他认识你吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.79,0:22:31.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不认识  在诊所那儿他没看见我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  你现在就是加调局探员了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.48,0:22:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要一起去吗  说不定挺好玩儿的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:40.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不去了  我还有别的事要处理
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.54,0:22:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-到时再碰头吧  -行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.99,0:22:43.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次别失手了  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.00,0:22:46.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是  长官
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.67,0:23:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,里德·史密斯探员
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.15,0:23:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在吗  范佩尔探员派我来的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:50.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.67,0:23:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奥斯卡·科德罗探员  加调局的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.88,0:23:58.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来接你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.29,0:24:10.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得保证我安全
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.49,0:24:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.43,0:24:15.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.17,0:24:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:20.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,天呐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.18,0:24:21.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到车尾去
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.38,0:24:42.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会真以为你能逃脱得了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.28,0:24:50.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你懂事的  帮个忙  自己爬后备箱里去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.80,0:24:52.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再让我歇会儿  行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.80,0:24:54.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到后备箱里去歇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.54,0:24:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别逼我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.47,0:25:07.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上车
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.44,0:25:23.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有个条件  我要求完全豁免权
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.33,0:25:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除非你们放过我  否则我一个字都不会说的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.77,0:25:25.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.23,0:25:27.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.81,0:25:29.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站起来走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.28,0:25:31.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过但愿你能在你的朋友追上你之前
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.90,0:25:33.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走出这栋大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.74,0:25:35.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要你坦白我们所要的信息
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.79,0:25:38.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我保证把你安排在远离加州的
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.09,0:25:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦监狱
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.57,0:25:42.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保证你安全
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.60,0:25:52.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五年前  我伤了背
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.38,0:25:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为了帮我表兄搬张该死的沙发
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.02,0:25:58.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,医生给我开了点儿止痛片
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.61,0:26:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,结果我欲罢不能
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.29,0:26:02.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我上瘾了  自己都没觉察到
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.31,0:26:03.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:03.88,0:26:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.00,0:26:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在卡森泉把一个小混混
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.52,0:26:10.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逼到了一条巷子里  然后我的瘾上来了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.13,0:26:13.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全意识不清了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.32,0:26:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我以为有人跟踪我
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.70,0:26:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开枪打死了一个小女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:24.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她十二岁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.16,0:26:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当地警察采了我的血样
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.73,0:26:31.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们有目击证人  我当时死定了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.65,0:26:34.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后来了个警探
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.61,0:26:36.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他找到我说
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.57,0:26:38.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们可以把这事摆平
Dialogue: 0,0:26:39.10,0:26:40.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后真的摆平了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.34,0:26:43.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血样  目击证人  都摆平了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.24,0:26:45.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们摆平那事儿以后
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.56,0:26:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局还给我颁发了一枚奖章呢
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.22,0:26:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"他们"到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.76,0:26:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们自称为"布莱克组织"
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.95,0:27:00.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.50,0:27:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老虎  老虎  燃烧着煌煌的火光
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.75,0:27:06.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}此处摘自郭沫若译本
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.47,0:27:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来自布莱克的诗作
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.12,0:27:14.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概某人很喜欢他的作品吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.25,0:27:16.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织里还有些什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.00,0:27:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警察  法官  联调局探员
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.17,0:27:20.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任何一个有秘密需要掩盖的执法人员
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.85,0:27:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如你的毒瘾
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.64,0:27:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当你有麻烦了  向他们求助
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.19,0:27:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当他们让你做点什么  你就得照做
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.12,0:27:29.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"老虎  老虎"
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.83,0:27:31.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.53,0:27:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,组织有头目吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.00,0:27:36.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定有
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.73,0:27:39.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我不知道是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.61,0:27:41.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我只知道我所接触的小团体
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.43,0:27:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过我猜测
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.58,0:27:47.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,整个组织至少有数百人  甚至上千人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.29,0:27:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道就没人发觉这一切吗
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.25,0:27:53.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鲍勃·柯克兰知道这事  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.58,0:27:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快直接招了吧  说出来给你自己一个解脱
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.08,0:28:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.71,0:28:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他知道的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.92,0:28:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我杀了他
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.79,0:28:11.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.10,0:28:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是布莱克组织的成员吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.49,0:28:25.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.73,0:28:28.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰有一个追随者
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.17,0:28:30.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丽贝卡·安德森
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.54,0:28:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四年前杀了几个你们的人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.30,0:28:35.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  山姆·博斯科和他的小队
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.12,0:28:35.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是他们
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.49,0:28:39.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人曾要我搞到联调局证件
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.98,0:28:42.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以便他们能进入加调局
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.62,0:28:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰或者他的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.73,0:28:49.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,潜入加调局  对丽贝卡下毒
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.48,0:28:51.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你竟然为他们提供了帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.44,0:28:54.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那时我才知道
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.17,0:28:57.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是在帮助一个连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.29,0:29:00.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是谁让你搞那些证件的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.50,0:29:02.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道  我只是接到一通电话
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.18,0:29:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是组织的运作方式
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.16,0:29:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你永远不知道上线是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.45,0:29:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.53,0:29:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们能保证我的安全 对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.30,0:29:15.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那要看情况了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.25,0:29:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你杀害了我的妻子和女儿吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.36,0:29:26.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没有杀你的妻子和女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.35,0:29:29.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,以我母亲的名义起誓
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.34,0:29:40.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你相信他吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.82,0:29:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他承认了谋杀罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.94,0:29:43.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血腥约翰绝不会这么容易崩溃
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.46,0:29:44.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即便是做戏也不会如此
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.47,0:29:45.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果史密斯不是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.93,0:29:47.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就意味着我们还得继续追查
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.46,0:29:48.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们需要帮助
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.28,0:29:49.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁是布伦达·夏垂克的继任者
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.60,0:29:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公共关系部吗  干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.93,0:29:53.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非常感谢大家能在临时通知后赶来
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.84,0:29:56.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位是加调局顾问派翠克·简
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.50,0:29:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他将就血腥约翰一案的进展
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.46,0:30:00.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进行通报
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.63,0:30:03.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.54,0:30:05.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,十年前
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.40,0:30:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被称作血腥约翰的连环杀手
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.47,0:30:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀害了我的妻子和女儿
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.43,0:30:13.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自那以后  我们一直在全力追捕他
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.98,0:30:15.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天我们很高兴地宣布
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.33,0:30:18.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们终于确认了他的身份与面目
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.70,0:30:22.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,执法部门负责人
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.02,0:30:24.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盖尔·伯特仑局长  就是血腥约翰
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.00,0:30:27.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他持有武器  极度危险
Dialogue: 0,0:30:27.56,0:30:30.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人发现他的行踪  切勿靠近
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.79,0:30:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请立即致电加利福尼亚州调查局
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.48,0:30:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.48,0:30:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请轮流提问
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.72,0:30:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉请回避  女士
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.14,0:31:02.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能谈谈这事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.35,0:31:04.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.52,0:31:06.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,关于伯特仑是血腥约翰的事
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.58,0:31:07.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来就是他
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.20,0:31:10.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果让简找到他  简会杀了他的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.06,0:31:11.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.46,0:31:15.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我们就没问题吗  把顶头上司杀了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.78,0:31:17.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-我无所谓  -我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.35,0:31:19.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.81,0:31:21.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要我们保持步调统一
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.08,0:31:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就是觉得有点诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.95,0:31:34.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特仑吸烟吗
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.69,0:31:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不吸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.25,0:31:38.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有时候人们会收到打火机作为礼物
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.60,0:31:47.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩尔
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.83,0:31:53.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个闪存盘
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.72,0:31:54.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们来瞧瞧
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.57,0:31:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}纳帕谷  七仙女酒厂
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.08,0:31:57.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,盘里只有一个文件
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.62,0:31:58.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有密码保护
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.98,0:32:00.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得硬破解
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.92,0:32:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,棒极了  我一直想用用我的新FPGA
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.92,0:32:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}[FPGA: 现场可编程逻辑门排列]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:03.75,0:32:04.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的什么
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.84,0:32:06.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信我  还是别问了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.03,0:32:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}加州调查局  内部数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.32,0:32:11.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.97,0:32:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.33,0:32:14.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}加州调查局  内部数据库
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.10,0:32:15.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}[乱码]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.28,0:32:18.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,该死的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.12,0:32:19.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起来像个清单
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.64,0:32:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会不会是名单  你能破译吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.01,0:32:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先试试看
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.43,0:32:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但破解谜题是简的任务
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.66,0:32:27.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到时候发给他
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.02,0:32:34.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来一杯这个  这种威士忌口感很纯
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.57,0:32:35.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用了很多泥煤烘烤麦芽
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.98,0:32:43.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很不错  能加点冰块吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.74,0:32:46.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你确定吗  这可是上好的苏格兰威士忌
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.09,0:32:49.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我确定
Dialogue: 0,0:33:01.12,0:33:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家伙跟你有点像
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.44,0:33:06.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b1\bord1\shad1\3c&H2F2F2F&}连环杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.51,0:33:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我需要一辆车
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.89,0:33:48.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们在去酒吧的路上了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.19,0:33:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高速巡警封锁了高速公路
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.89,0:33:51.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只要他一跑我们就能抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.28,0:33:52.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但他要是躲起来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.50,0:33:54.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特仑在柑橘高地杀了个酒保
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.54,0:33:56.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在那边的姨妈有间房子
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.21,0:33:57.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你觉得他在那里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.71,0:33:59.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她六个月之前搬到养老院去了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.81,0:34:01.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以她家现在空着
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.33,0:34:03.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听起来是个不错的藏身之处  地址在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.50,0:34:05.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露丝玛丽街1408号
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.44,0:34:07.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们就到  让周和快速反应小组过去
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.73,0:34:09.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,准备好直升机
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.30,0:34:27.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他在这吗  -在那里面
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.05,0:34:28.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让卡尔和几个人去后面了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.42,0:34:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他无处可逃  -我们能信他们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.95,0:34:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看了他们的肩膀  没有纹身
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.42,0:34:38.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这里干什么  我没叫萨城警局派特警
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.25,0:34:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人要我们来的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.57,0:34:41.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那边建一个指挥中心
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.74,0:34:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听着  各位  这里由我负责
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.38,0:34:44.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们是从北区来的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.65,0:34:47.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都跨了整个城了  到底是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.54,0:34:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是他干的  他把他们叫来的
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.71,0:34:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伯特仑把特警叫到自己这来干嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.53,0:34:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不止召来了一个特警组
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.15,0:34:56.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他把整个特警队都召来了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.10,0:34:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一片混乱
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.00,0:35:00.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,屋后有整整一队别的警察在准备
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.44,0:35:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们无法控制局面了  头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.88,0:35:04.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他在他们之中  伯特仑混在他们之中
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.90,0:35:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他要逃跑  我们得停止行动
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.22,0:35:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁都不许走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.17,0:35:13.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一个人都不许走
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.83,0:35:51.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.82,0:36:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得吃点东西
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.45,0:36:02.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要吃中餐么  我知道有一家很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.64,0:36:05.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  听起来不错
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.47,0:36:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们在屋里发现了伯特仑的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.15,0:36:13.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该是有人在他去之前
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.92,0:36:15.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在房子里放好了特警服
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.06,0:36:16.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把城里所有的特警和
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.55,0:36:17.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快速反应小组叫了过去
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.90,0:36:19.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道是谁打的电话吗
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.79,0:36:21.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是个能在暗中一呼百应的人
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.65,0:36:23.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,布莱克组织
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.52,0:36:25.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,头儿
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.78,0:36:28.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请各位注意一下
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.16,0:36:31.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放下电话  离开你们的桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.87,0:36:32.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.67,0:36:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这里特别探员主管特蕾莎·里斯本
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.72,0:36:36.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你又是哪位
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.22,0:36:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局监管部门探员  丹尼斯·阿尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.85,0:36:44.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再说一遍  站起来
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.32,0:36:46.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,离开桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.67,0:36:48.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.13,0:36:50.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们正在追捕
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.20,0:36:52.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一名极其危险的逃犯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.18,0:36:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你们想协助
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.95,0:36:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们这个所谓的执法部门的长官
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.27,0:36:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是个杀人犯
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.88,0:37:01.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是重大犯罪组织的一员
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.69,0:37:05.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个组织里也有联调局探员
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.03,0:37:06.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对  所以局里把我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.75,0:37:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从德州奥斯汀调过来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.84,0:37:10.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,收拾你们这个烂摊子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.64,0:37:16.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我手里有一份
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.02,0:37:19.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联邦法官签署的令状
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.53,0:37:24.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,联调局将立即关停你们部门
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.63,0:37:26.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所有人
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.54,0:37:30.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,解除任职
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.40,0:37:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,立即生效
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.23,0:37:32.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不能这么做
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是来收集证据的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.46,0:37:37.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要妨碍我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.62,0:37:39.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大伙开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.72,0:37:58.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.42,0:38:00.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.63,0:38:06.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是联调局的丹尼斯·阿尔伯特
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.07,0:38:07.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一定是派翠克·简了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.40,0:38:08.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们关停了我们部门
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.66,0:38:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们到时候会找你问话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.55,0:38:12.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过可以缓一缓  我们会在这儿待一阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.57,0:38:14.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别出城
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.77,0:38:17.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们还有个凶手要抓
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.20,0:38:18.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这案子现在归我们管了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.95,0:38:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你有过机会  但是搞砸了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.99,0:38:22.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果你当时是真想抓他的话
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.76,0:38:34.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是我最喜欢的杯子
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.87,0:38:41.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  幸会  再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.61,0:38:48.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.74,0:38:50.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.85,0:38:53.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,范佩尔在伯特仑的闪存里找到了一些加密文件
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.64,0:38:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要不要从那开始查
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.71,0:38:57.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了  浪费时间而已  结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.58,0:38:59.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里没我们的事儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.40,0:39:02.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家吧  休息一下
